name: Self Portrait As Van Gogh
description: This work was using with analog to digital method, sources analog works in the photogram technique in the Raw Power art project, then collated through digital animation. This self portrait, begins with  self portrait as  Man Ray and physical work is exhibited at  artjog Time (to) Wonder with Ruang MES 56 in On Heavy Rotation in 2021. The photogram collage in analog-digital that I created, is my way of imagining what I want to be. In this context, I imagine being an influential artist in the art world.
